  "keyFeatures": [
    "Guided Architectural Workflow (Context → Requirements → Architecture → UX/UI → Planning)",
    "RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) over a curated technical knowledge base",
    "Local-First Privacy Mode using Ollama for 100% offline AI processing",
    "Hybrid LLM support: Ollama (local) and Groq/Gemini (cloud) providers",
    "Tech Packs for stack-specific architecture rules (Flutter, Python, Firebase)",
    "Context Factory generating AGENTS.md and RULES.md for AI copilots",
    "Flutter Desktop frontend (Linux/Windows/macOS)",
    "FastAPI + LangChain backend with streaming chat responses",
    "ChromaDB vector store for semantic knowledge retrieval",
    "Docker Compose one-command deployment in under 2 minutes"
